snippet.title: LEGO™ Bricktales | Announce Teaser Trailer l Meta Quest 2 + Meta Quest 3
snippet.description: The critically acclaimed puzzle-game LEGO™ Bricktales is coming to Meta Quest 7th December 2023. Pre-order now to receive an exclusive outfit: https://metaque.st/3LE6rX6
